1 unit(s) Passion Fruit
1 pack(s) Coconut Milk
1 unit(s) Mango
110 grams Yoghurt
125 grams Blueberries
60 grams Granola
to taste Water
to taste Sugar

Halve the passion fruit.
Peel the mango and remove the pit. Chop into 1cm pieces.

Blend the mango with coconut milk and yoghurt.
Loosen with a splash of water and add sugar to taste, if required.

Divide the smoothie between bowls.
Top with the passion fruit halves, blueberries and granola.